    "body": "We do not support sending unsigned transactions in Besu. You can either send a signed transaction using [eth_sendRawTransaction](https://besu.hyperledger.org/en/stable/Reference/API-Methods/#eth_sendrawtransaction) or otherwise use a transaction signer, such as EthSigner, to send your transaction. For more information on how to do that, see this docs page:  https://docs.ethsigner.pegasys.tech/en/stable/HowTo/Transactions/Make-Transactions/#eth_sendtransaction",
